{
  "stem": "10587.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in our hometown, there was mainly Jewish organizations, like the girls belonged to the Bais Yaakov [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brothers, Ramek and Herman maybe to one of the men's organizations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gredonia ?] yeah, or-- something-- but I-- they were-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they-- they were organizations that were mainly [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] connected somehow with Israel.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Zionist-- Zionist organizations.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember going to a movie, ever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I'm sure there must have been some movies in town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, especially which was the-- I remember reading about it more, and also pictures in the paper than the movies because we didn't-- there was no-- you didn't have a television.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, there was-- there was Yiddish music, Yiddish theater, which I-- I have not seen it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because-- but I know that there was comedies like [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [INAUDIBLE]-- I can't really think of too many of those.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was disbanded because they-- you could not congregate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jews were not allowed to-- to congregate in a group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No question.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was aware of it before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was aware that what was happening in Germany, that the Jews were being-- being persecuted, and when they burned the books and they-- and where they demolished all the Jewish businesses and stores and some-- and the synagogues were destroyed.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very well aware of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I saw our temple burning, when-- when the-- when the Germans burned it in 1940.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt like, how could this happen?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why-- why-- why this-- God letting this happen?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our-- our place of worship, this is-- you know, the main-- the main synagogue of town, which has been-- I don't know exactly how old it was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was a nice and beautiful synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- a-- there were other synagogues-- there were other [INAUDIBLE], what they called, and also house of prayers, mainly [INAUDIBLE], where more Hasidic than ultra Orthodox people would-- would go.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Synagogue was already more sort of, I would, say reform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was maybe a little bit more modern because it was a beautiful structure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It had [INAUDIBLE] and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A [INAUDIBLE] usually had benches and tables and maybe a little credenza to hold the Sefer Torah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But-- or some kind of a arc, but the synagogue had to be beautiful [INAUDIBLE] with the arc with the-- in the Sefer Torah.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt like-- like-- like the-- this is a place where I was going to pray, where I was going to school and learn about the [INAUDIBLE], Russia and-- and about the five books of Moses, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that this-- what am I going to do now?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where-- where-- where do I go from here?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I felt like I was-- there was a terrible violation to-- to my education.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was going to public school, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was going to elementary school, which was total opposite direction from the-- from the synagogue, but since we were so centrally located, so for me it was maybe a little bit further to the public school, but we-- then-- then went to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Synagogue was very close.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, the schools-- no, you were not allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't even think that the schools were open.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after the Germans occupied our town, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I think the learning ceased to exist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was bar mitzvah'd in the basement of my grandfather's house, and-- and many people came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was not-- never the same as what would have really happened in our main-- in our temple, main sanctuary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] sorry--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- I studied very hard because I want my parents to be proud of me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I also wanted to do a good job, because the-- of-- of what has been happening, to continue with my-- to carry on my-- my Jewish tradition.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I worked harder and I-- I struggled, and I-- I don't personally remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was told that I did a very good job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents were very proud of me for doing what I did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was with candle lights, or-- and-- and those-- those-- the lights that you have with gasoline.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A gas lamp with the cylinder, glass cylinder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- not actually gas, but it was gasoline type, you know, like, they call it naphtha, I remember, in Polish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how I remember having my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Top secret, in top secret.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
